1. *Širi* se vest da će biti padavina narednih dana. (The news is *spreading* that there will be precipitation in the coming days.)
2. Vidim da si se *širio* poslednjih meseci, izgledaš odlično. (I see you've *expanded* in the last few months, you look great.)
3. On je veoma uticajan i *širi* svoj uticaj širom zemlje. (He's very influential and *spreading* his influence across the country.)
4. Kada mi je bilo hladno, *širio* sam ruke da bih se zagrejao. (When I was cold, I *spread* my arms to warm up.)
5. Ova tema se *široko* *širi* u poslednje vreme i mnogi ljudi razgovaraju o njoj. (This topic is *widely* *spreading* recently and many people are talking about it.)
6. Oni žele da *prošire* svoj posao na drugu zemlju. (They want to *expand* their business to another country.)
7. Danas učimo kako *proširiti* rečnik na engleskom jeziku. (Today we're learning how to *enlarge* our vocabulary in English.)
8. Nakon uspešnog lansiranja, kompanija planira da *proširi* proizvodnju. (After a successful launch, the company plans to *extend* production.)